column6: Location determined using the Global Positioning System. http://www.gps.gov/
Location determined using the frequency shift of transmissions to the ARGOS communications satellite service. http://www.argos-system.org/web/en/333-why-choose-argos.php
Location determined using the frequency shift of transmissions to the Iridium communications satellite constellation. https://www.iridium.com/
Location determined using the Kalman filtering technique and the ARGOS communications satellite service. http://www.argos-system.org/web/en/393-faq-kalman.php.
Location determined using the European GALILEO global navigation satellite system. http://galileognss.eu/
Location determined using the LORAN (LOng RAnge Navigation) hyperbolic radio system.
Location determined using a geographic survey.
Location extracted by locating the object on a map.
